{
  "texts": [
    "It involves crafting the input text (or prompt) to guide the model in generating a desired output.",
    "Through effective prompt engineering, users can steer the focus of LLMs and improve the quality of the extracted information.",
    "Moreover, LLMs like Llama 2 can perform zero-shot learning, which allows the model to make predictions or generate responses in tasks it has not explicitly been trained on.",
    "Contrarily, few-shot learning for LLMs refers to the process of a model learning from a small number of examples.",
    "For a specific task, we can provide a few demonstrative examples in the prompt to enhance the performance through few-shot learning."
  ]
}